Osmond’s Horizon to Buy APR for $850 Million, Telegraph Reports

-- B y   L a n a n h   N g u y e n
-- 
2011-06-12T07:17:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/osmond-s-horizon-to-buy-apr-for-850-million-telegraph-reports.html
Hugh Osmond’s Horizon Acquisition
Co. is in talks to buy a 60 percent stake in power supplier  APR
Energy  for $850 million, the Sunday Telegraph said, without
saying where it got the information.  The cash and shares purchase may be announced as early as
tomorrow following final negotiations this weekend, according to
the newspaper.  A spokesman for Horizon declined to comment, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
